title: BONUS: Velvet's Edge with Kelly Henderson - Demarcus Family Rules with Allison and Jay Demarcus
itunes:title: BONUS: Velvet's Edge with Kelly Henderson - Demarcus Family Rules with Allison and Jay Demarcus
description:
Check out Velvet's Edge with Kelly Henderson!

Kelly Henderson talks to Rascal Flatts member, Jay Demarcus and his wife, Allison, about their new Netflix reality show, Demarcus Family Rules. The couple also gives the surprising story of how they met and got together, tells why therapy has saved their marriage multiple times and reveals whether or not they will have any more kids.
